3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): The paper may be relevant to computer vision applications that involve attitude estimation from inertial measurements. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper may be relevant to machine learning applications that involve attitude estimation from inertial measurements.
